                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
                                    <div>Application design, architecture development, and implementation</div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
                                    <div>User interface design and web development</div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
                                    <div>Software Product Development</div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
