                                    <div>Systems integration and consolidation</div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
                                    <div>Re-engineering, migration, modernization, performance tuning</div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h2 py-10">Our Application Management solutions include:</div>
                        <div class="diff-description">
                            <ul>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
                                    <div> Application Development</div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pb-2">
                                    <img src="/svg/list.svg" class="pt-[6px]" alt="bullet list" width="12" height="12" />
